sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as User
    participant App as App Process
    participant Srv as Lanthing Server
    participant Svc as Service Process
    participant Sess as WorkerSession
    participant Wkr as Worker Process
    participant Sig as Signaling Service
    participant Cli as Client Process
    participant Tp as Transport RTC/TCP

    User->>App: Launch app and request remote control
    App->>Srv: RequestConnection(peerDeviceID, token)

    Srv->>Svc: OpenConnection(streaming params)
    Svc->>Sess: Create session from open request
    Sess->>Wkr: Start worker process(action=streaming)
    Wkr-->>Sess: Worker ready (pipe + capabilities)
    Svc-->>Srv: OpenConnectionAck
    Srv-->>App: RequestConnectionAck

    par Signaling join
        Sess->>Sig: Join room as controlled side
    and Requester side startup
        App->>Cli: Spawn client process with params
        Cli->>Sig: Join room as requester side
    end

    Sig-->>Sess: SignalingMessage(candidate/sdp)
    Sig-->>Cli: SignalingMessage(candidate/sdp)
    Sess->>Tp: Build server transport(RTC/RTC2/TCP)
    Cli->>Tp: Build client transport(RTC/RTC2/TCP)
    Tp-->>Sess: Connected(link type)
    Tp-->>Cli: Connected(link type)

    Cli->>Sess: StartTransmission
    Sess-->>Cli: StartTransmissionAck

    loop Streaming session
        Wkr->>Sess: Encoded video/audio frames
        Sess->>Cli: Media frames over transport
        Cli-->>Sess: Input events + control messages
        Sess-->>Cli: Cursor/stat/keepalive updates
    end

    alt Disconnect or error
        Cli->>Sess: Close / transport failed
        Sess->>Svc: Session closed(reason)
        Svc->>App: DisconnectedConnection notification
    else Continue
        Sess-->>Cli: KeepAliveAck
    end